name: Realistic Futa
description:
"I respect everyone, not because of their gender, but because everyone has a free soul"

I do know there are detailed definitions of Futa about whether they have vagina, penis and testicles at the same time or not. But, honestly, too detailed definitions will merely frighten the audience who do not know them, which is harmful for the community.

Besides, "realistic" means realistical generations but not "real", i do not suggest anyone who use it to violate the law and jeopardize others.

Very appreciated for reviews, glad to receive more :D

Ver.1

Dreamlike license

Credit to:

The Realistic Futa generation model is inspired by Futagen made by stablydiffused and is based on Art & Eros (aEros) - A tribute to beauty made by aine_captain , AIroticArt's Penis Model made by airoticart.

How to get this model:

Roughly similiar as Futagen, using AIroticArt's Penis Model to let the other realistic based model know what is " futanari : the woman with penis". After processing, then blend it with Futagen, the consistent futanari but its style is more anime and cartoon.

Prompt recommendation:

Largely same as Futagen

Penis, frenulum, penerec, erect penis

p.s.

  1. Using "futanari woman" but not "girl" , because girl contains latent information about female genitial which may distort with penis in weird chaos.

  2. Naked body will have more consistent output, better more with "spread legs" added.

  3. Interesting thing is that you may not put "pussy, vagina" into negative prompt.
    Why? I guess because this is how the algorithm learn the concept, futanari, to substitute pussy with penis, so pussy here provide important location related info which tell the model where penis should be.

Limitation:

  1. Cannot generate consistent and decent futa output when one or more clothes prompt exist.


    Temporary solution:

    1. Try to use "AND" prompt grammar in Stable Diffusion, as it works to add two separate things together. So you may get a futa with clothes.

    2. Using impaint "DDIM" sampler to re-paint clothes but remain penis as the original

  2. "Spread legs" or the other sex related prompt may blend penis in anal with penis on your futa, so you need toy it around serveral times. (But if you like it..... :D )

Update 02/02/2023

Limitation 1: Cannot generate futa with clothes.

Example outputs: The first picture with black blouse.

Solution:

Using "Prompt Substitution", "Composable-Diffusion", details in Prompt Editing.

I will not dive too deep within the grammar, cuz it needs some time and practices with specific model. Then you can understand what prompt is the most suitable one.

To be brief, With prompt grammar we can firstly render male and then we render Futa.

Interesting thing is here. Algorithm will reserve space for male's penis because Algorithm take male's penis as granted but not the Futa's. So the interaction between penis and clothes is kept through male.

And through "Prompt Substitution", we can retain penis by using Futanari woman with .....(descriptive words about penis)... but add more Feminine adjectives at the same time to shift shape of male body into female.

As the output show, penis looks even better than directly rendering a Futa's penis (it may look very similiar but the way they comes from are totally different.). And clothes looks well too.

Hope this can help. :D

Enjoy~
